name: 奥斯汀·亚诺斯基
name_full: 奥斯汀·亚诺斯基 Austin Janowsky

last_movies.title: 爱/恨:漫画艺术家的奇妙人生！
阿尔玛·菲尔丁的恐怖之家

introduction: Austin Janowsky is an American actor-screenwriter-director. He has been told he has a "Great Face" by Bruce Cambell. A Meisner trained actor with Lee Perkins, he enjoys being a character actor. He has been fortunate enough to work on films like 45 Seconds with Obba Babatunde, Dark my Light with Albert Jones and Tom Lipinski. Epiphany with Caitlin Carmichael, George Georgiou and in Dan Myrick and Jeffrey Reddick's new Episodic series "Black Veil".Austin Janowsky has also work as a comic book artist since 1994 for Marvel Comics, Image Comics, IDW, Dynamite Ent. Devils Due and others. Janowsky's most recent comic is his all age holiday series "Stanley The Snowman" with Scout Comics.Austin Janowsky grew up in Upstate NY - New Hartford, NY. He is the son of Ron and Kay Janowsky. Austin was in musicals and theater is entire school career and being named "Most Theatrical" his senior year. After he graduated, He moved to Florida where he lives by the ocean with his Wife. He has 4 adult children.Janowsky loves to travel for work and is an avid poker player.
